column5: Great Video, love it!  Any father's out there can relate to you. The feeling you get when you see the excitement on your boys face when he is hauling in a fish is priceless. Great times. Cheers,
Awesome as always Simon! He's casting like a pro! HH
Your videos and pics always put a smile on my face.    Great times with Jack, boy is he growing and fishing like a pro!!  Thanks for the report Simon!

He's kicking butt out in the bush! Good job dad
